\par \pard\plain \s253\li120\sb120\sa60\sl-240 \b\f6\fs20\lang1033 Close Articles
\par \pard\plain \li115\sb80\sl-240 \f6\fs20\lang1033 Closes all open {\uldb Article windows}{\v article_window}.
\par \pard\plain \s253\li120\sb120\sa60\sl-240 \b\f6\fs20\lang1033 Close Groups
\par \pard\plain \li115\sb80\sl-240 \f6\fs20\lang1033 Closes all open {\uldb Group windows}{\v group_window}.
\par \pard\plain \s253\li120\sb120\sa60\sl-240 \b\f6\fs20\lang1033 Close Status
\par \pard\plain \li115\sb80\sl-240 \f6\fs20\lang1033 Closes all open Status windows.
\par \pard\plain \s253\li120\sb120\sa60\sl-240 \b\f6\fs20\lang1033 Send Posts
\par \pard\plain \li115\sb80\sl-240 \f6\fs20\lang1033 Sends all {\ul postings}{\v posting} in open {\uldb Posting windows}{\v posting_window}.
\par \pard\plain \s253\li120\sb120\sa60\sl-240 \b\f6\fs20\lang1033 Send Mails
\par \pard\plain \li115\sb80\sl-240 \f6\fs20\lang1033 Sends all {\ul electronic mail messages}{\v electronic_mail_message} in open {\uldb Mail windows}{\v mail_window}.
